    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-080__align-001">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-080</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 80.1 - 老子 80.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 80.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>小國寡民，使有什伯之器而不用，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In a little state with a small population, I would so order it, that, though there were individuals with the abilities of ten or a hundred men, there should be no employment of them;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-080__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-080</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 80.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 80.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>使民重死而不遠徙。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I would make the people, while looking on death as a grievous thing, yet not remove elsewhere (to avoid it).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
