      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 80.13 - 老子 80.16</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 80.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鄰國相望，雞犬之聲相聞，民至老死，不相往來。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There should be a neighbouring state within sight, and the voices of the fowls and dogs should be heard all the way from it to us, but I would make the people to old age, even to death, not have any intercourse with it.</seg>
      </tuv>
